</span></p></dd><dd><dl class='nested'><dt><a class='title-link' name='name' href='#name'></a> name</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>The name to use for the thermostat.</p>
</span></p></dd><dd><dl class='nested'><dt><a class='title-link' name='mac' href='#mac'></a> mac</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>MAC address of the thermostat.</p>
